  "comment": {
    "text": "This is the description for the OAuth card on the Developer Tools page. It explains that the OAuth API allows third-party applications to access user data and perform actions within DocSpace. `{{organizationName}}` is the name of the organization, and `{{productName}}` is the name of the product (e.g., ONLYOFFICE DocSpace).",
